title: FOREIGN TALENTS SLEEPING OUTSIDE HOUSE, TOO TIRED AFTER HARD WORK
text:
FOREIGN TALENTS SLEEPING OUTSIDE HOUSE, TOO TIRED AFTER HARD WORK Submitted by farhan on 
Dear A.S.S. Editor Advertisement 
This is what we saw outside our neighbour's unit this morning at 7.30 am on Sunday morning. 
Clearly they are foreign talent who have labored so hard to create jobs for Singaporeans that they have forgotten to find a roof over their heads under which to spend the night. 
Bernard Tan
